Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was divorced three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be precise, my wife left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I spent most of my \N time listening to what was said here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and not to what my wife said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're just a collector who peers into human minds."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The task of peering into the deep abyss \N and lurking in the depths of the human mind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,puts me at the inherent risk of sinking into the abyss myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, your fourth victim was an \N eighteen year old Munich woman, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you cut her up, did you become sexually aroused?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask me about my twelfth victim instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be Ms. Hanna Kempf from the Klopp House,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fifty two years old, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it was her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll ask you about it at some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but right now, I wanted to ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about the one before, the eleventh case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let me ask you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you feel sexual excitement
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before killing the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{fad(0,40)}or after?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:01.20,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,314)\fad(300,84)}Abyss of the Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As previously stated, the victims were limited to girls
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with long hair, between the ages of sixteen and eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This case definitely should \N be categorized as sexual murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he has also confessed to the twelfth case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, the victim, Ms. Kempf, was 52 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there was no evidence of sexual assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, by stating that he \N committed this murder at the request of a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he has confused the investigation--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you scared me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the only way I could come visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know why, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe that I am a serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell from newspaper articles,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stuff on TV, and rumors from \N former university classmates alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you come to visit me, of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as though we were particularly good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, you looked down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I thought, every time our eyes met.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you looked down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to repay what I \N owed you from that time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.  That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're an authority on criminal psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like for you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Look at me!  Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster in me has grown this big, Dr. Tenma!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Help!  The monster within me is about to explode!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this Johan was the one \N who killed the hospital director,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then killed each of his former foster parents, one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and disappeared again after leaving this message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must find him as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thereby prove your innocence as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years ago in the medical \N sciences department of a certain university,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a man who had to be number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, a Japanese man transferred in, \N and the man's position changed completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese man was social \N and become popular right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, he received good \N marks and easily dislodged the man
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from first place in the first semester exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,became desperate to regain his \N position in the second semester exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He performed perfectly in all his subjects up to that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the last test
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was on general forensic medicine, the \N subject in which he was the least capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he failed that test, all of his \N efforts up to then would be wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He decided on a last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Now, I'll be number one."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Japanese man didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the man made a great \N comeback and regained first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:07:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is there anything you can \N figure out from these two messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he has the multiple \N personality disorder you spoke of, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to say that one \N personality is committing these murders
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that a different personality is trying to prevent them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, there have been serial homicides
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in which notes like these were left at the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these notes can be an \N "excuse" in order to escape culpability.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making the distinction between the two \N possibilities is where our skills as psychoanalysts come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people mistakenly believe \N that serial killers are introverted,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that is completely inaccurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those who are highly \N intelligent, sociable, and smooth spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are compulsive liars, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,toying with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hang on there.  It's unwise to leap to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you speak about Johan in more detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually divorced three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be precise, my wife left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an interesting story, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to do a complete study on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please contact me in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand him well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On what points?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"monster" that he spoke of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the monster exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does exist indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in you, in him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and also in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an armchair theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that a monster exists in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like being looked down on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-the guards...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are things in the world that are more terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will definitely come to see you, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you right away when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:10:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like for him to become one of my \N research subjects after you arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is an extremely interesting criminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Ms. Kempf's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The basement storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go there, you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that a monster exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'd love to meet with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Detective Köhl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've promised to meet up with Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's at 8 o'clock this evening \N in front of the fountain in Oder Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am currently retracing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the route Jurgens took to break \N into the house on the day of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to his statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he hid in this storage room, and spent a few hours there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then immediately after Ms. Kempf returned home,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he forced his way into the second floor bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing unusual about this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some framed photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,include Ms. Kempf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing that would prove the existence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the monster Jurgens mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I'd thought, he committed the twelfth murder
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to confuse the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stated that he committed \N the crime at a friend's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By calling that friend a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my mom would punish me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a large doll that my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,really treasured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl doll with long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:13:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would ask the doll to help me as my mom beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doll would only smirk at me as it watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That storage room was full of my mom's pictures, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where I looked, \N it was my mom, mom, mom, mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would be watching me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like the room he described.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Jurgens recreate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the storage room from his childhood here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jurgens when he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never had any contact with \N Ms. Kempf during his childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jurgens' face was added on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Kempf had no children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that a monster exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just did exactly what was written in my friend's letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-friend...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a white envelope that didn't \N have the sender's name or address.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I was irritated
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the peculiar friendly letter, \N in which he said he understood me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the letters started coming every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started looking forward to these letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those letters were fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he might actually be a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the letter told me to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It told me to go to a storage room in a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The storage room in Ms. Kempf's mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how he knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he knew about my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At. Ms. Kempf's mansion, I became disoriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Ms. Kempf...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I regained my senses, I \N was already on the second floor and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His friend also sent letters to Ms. Kempf?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster in me has grown this big!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster within me is about to explode!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are messages that Johan left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight o'clock came and went a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Köhl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an Asian with longish hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you take time away from work, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to analyze what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they were all lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Johan didn't exist anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that he was an imaginary person you had thought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy, please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, I am studying a serial killer named Jurgens,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was one murder in which \N his methods differed from his usual ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to me instead of talking about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay folks, that's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The carnival is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to secure him at my signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to every single word of their conversation, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you looked down on me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you saw me cheating at the university,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've been looking down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Köhl,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Galen and Tenma are walking toward the west exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will mingle with the crowd of \N people going home after the carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I am someone who should be looked down on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy, now is not the time-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the cheat sheet hidden here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're surrounded by the police."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look.  Let's keep on walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the doctor being threatened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-well, the people around them are so \N noisy that we can't pick up their voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jurgens said that he killed Ms. Kempf at a friend's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in Ms. Kempf's storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Kempf didn't have any children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Johan you spoke of and the friend of Jurgens spoke of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are probably the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have passed through the west exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma may have a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same messages as Johan's
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were at Ms. Kempf's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan lived off of Ms. Kempf, \N then killed her when he didn't need her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be to erase his past, as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in any position to preach at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll tell you the result of my analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Johan can detect killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can infiltrate their solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and manipulate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, as to why you haven't \N found any cases where he murdered
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the foster parents he had when he was older...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he is at an age where he no longer needs foster parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other possible reasons, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan has finally found and joined
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ideal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, why does he try to erase his past?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason he needs to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then is he currently with \N a family for a particular purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To accomplish something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have arrived at the bus terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirm which bus he boards!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get cars to the terminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought the bus ticket for you in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is the option of giving yourself \N up, and then proving your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not pursuing Johan in order to prove my innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you aren't possibly thinking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't looking down on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you looked like an interesting guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't get a chance to get to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we've finally become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you saw me cheating...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You raised your head and looked toward me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was cheating too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five buses departed almost all at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma...
